<%= _('Hello %{name},') % { name: sanitize_name(@user.name) } %>

<%= s_('CompromisedPasswordDetection|The password used for your GitLab.com account %{username} may have been compromised due to a data breach on another service or platform. This does not necessarily mean that your GitLab account was accessed. However, leaving your password unchanged presents a significant security risk to your account.') % { username: @user.username } %>

<%= s_('CompromisedPasswordDetection|Please change your password immediately.') %>

<%= s_('CompromisedPasswordDetection|Failure to change your password may lead to temporary account access restrictions to prevent potential unauthorized access.') %>

<%= s_('CompromisedPasswordDetection|Instructions for changing your password can be found in the %{doc_link}.') % { doc_link: "#{s_('CompromisedPasswordDetection|GitLab documentation')} #{@url_to_change_password_docs}" } %>

<%= s_('CompromisedPasswordDetection|For your security, we also recommend enabling %{mfa_link} if you have not done so already.') % { mfa_link: "#{s_('CompromisedPasswordDetection|two-factor authentication')} #{@url_to_mfa_docs}" } %>

<%= _('Thank you,') %>

<%= _('GitLab Security') %>
